Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请 请快点投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.72,0:00:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.36,0:00:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.53,0:00:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得漂亮 美莉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.20,0:00:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有你 女王军便所向无敌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.12,0:00:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为操控超振动铠甲的先驱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.36,0:00:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你迟早会被大家交口称赞的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.87,0:00:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.01,0:01:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后也要好好表现哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
