Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.43,0:01:15.72,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}I was Born 泣きながら 生まれてきたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:20.93,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Why not 闘い得た　絆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.20,0:01:29.56,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Just now　この手の中で　熱く輝け
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.43,0:01:42.24,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}One in a seven billion の憂鬱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.42,0:01:47.80,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Someday 世界が終わる日が　来たって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.94,0:01:53.00,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}So，What？　1ミリの悔いもない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:58.72,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Say， yeah！！　一筋に走る流れ星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.90,0:02:01.38,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}鼓動ドキドキ止まれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.54,0:02:06.13,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}迷いも全部　蹴っ飛ばせ！！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.32,0:02:11.65,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}宇宙に　抱かれし　蒼い地球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:16.92,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}いつも心に描く　エリシオン
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:22.28,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}過去も未来も　自分が創る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.42,0:02:27.54,opjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}永遠の“Stellar”を見上げて
